--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages gnu_zip.

The gnu_zip package contains the popular GNU gnu_zip data compression program. Gzipped
files have a .gz extension.
Gzip should be installed on your system, because it is a very commonly used data
compression program.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: gnu_zip
    vars:
      gnu_zip_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: gnu_zip
    vars:
      gnu_zip_state: 'gnu_zip'

INACTIVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: gnu_zip
    vars:
      gnu_zip_state: 'inactive'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  gnu_zip_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install : 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove  : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
      Inactive: 'quiesce' | 'inactive'

